Crocodylia root of crown = 87.14 Ma, split with Aves = 240 (Zheng) => branch length = 152.86
Turtles root of crown = 209.23, split with Aves+Crocs = 265 (Zheng) => branch length = 55.77
Archosaurs root of crown =~ 300 & root of crown lepidosaurs~ 275 (Zheng) => Lepidosaurs branch length = 25

